      | username | firstname | lastname | email                | interests         |
      | manager1 | Manager   | 1        | manager1@example.com |                   |
      | user1    | User      | 1        | user1@example.com    | Cat,Dog,Turtle    |
      | editor1  | Editor    | 1        | editor1@example.com  |                   |
