      | name       | shortname |
      | Tag editor | tageditor |
    And the following "system role assigns" exist:
      | user     | course               | role      |
      | manager1 | Acceptance test site | manager   |
      | editor1  | Acceptance test site | tageditor |
    And the following "tags" exist:
